JOHANNESBURG – Women flooded social media on Friday with pictures of themselves wearing all black and doeks after a call by the ANC to honour Mama Winnie Madikizela-Mandela. The hashtag AllBlackWithADoek was trending. “Winnie Madikizela Mandela did not die. She multiplied,” the ANC said in a statement. My colleagues are within #AllBlackWithADoek pic.twitter.com/s1htNlxwER — Xolie ---- (@licy_tatsi) April 6, 2018 eNCA